{"tid":2434362,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"你地聽歌個app，開咗邊啲自己整嘅playlist？","createTime":"2021-03-05T12:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T15:06:18.000Z","uid":165817,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b1fab8784f0ab20386ba817a6b1a019351cc9d64","tid":2434362,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T12:58:17.000Z","msg":"佢本身係跟專輯或者歌手去分<br />\n但有時啲歌會有啲散<br />\n好多人都會自己整啲playlist<br />\n大家又開咗邊啲playlist?<br />\n<br />\n我自己嘅 廣東歌就有兩個<br />\n叱咤十大同四台冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n將攞過叱咤十大 同四台冠軍嘅放入去<br />\n<br />\n外語嘅就有幾個自己鍾意嘅歌手嘅CD歌<br />\n因為我都有好多演唱會版<br />\n所以開咗個專for佢地啲CD version<br />\n<br />\n你地呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa698c1fd03d57df3a2163c6732da844d9fb35e","tid":2434362,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:03:48.000Z","msg":"有張playlist專擺cover"},{"pid":"4fe75d2f47e9e60fd639942451477745e431c512","tid":2434362,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:08:15.000Z","msg":"乜文乜類型嘅歌都擺晒落同一個list <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e44b7b3a69ad4942fd8c9916182c128f16f87b","tid":2434362,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fe75d2f47e9e60fd639942451477745e431c512","tid":2434362,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:08:15.000Z","msg":"乜文乜類型嘅歌都擺晒落同一個list <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁開嚟做乜 你個app冇得「全部播放」咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2317ebd8abb3e7931dad85b74e346809c3343c","tid":2434362,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:14:29.000Z","m